        <Summary>Featureful client/server network backup suite</Summary>
        <Description>Bacula is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of computer data across a network of computers of different kinds. It is efficient and relatively easy to use, while offering many advanced storage management features that make it easy to find and recover lost or damaged files. Due to its modular design, Bacula is scalable from small single computer systems to networks of hundreds of machines.</Description>
